This Thing is SO BIG! | Breath of the Wild ►► https://goo.gl/iKjkbX
Watch MORE on the GTLive Channel! ►► http://bit.ly/1LkSBnz 
USE: #GTLIVE and @matpatgt to send us comments & questions!

It has been a long time since I've played a voice-controlled game, but I'm pumped to jump back in! Today, we're playing EIGHTH NOTE, a voice and sound activated game. Join us for this wacky episode where we'll try to play this funky game using everything from our voices to air horns!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

PlayDate from HELL! | Emily Wants to Play ► https://goo.gl/8m8cXn
Teaching Cars to KILL! | Moral Machine ► http://bit.ly/2gMZCT7
Weirdest Quiz Ever | Guess the Wikihow ► http://bit.ly/2gh4IpQSad Puppet is Sad! - FNAC Part 1 ►► http://bit.ly/1U8Xs0I
